<DocsLayout title="§16 AI Accountability" description="RCAN §16 — AI Accountability. Every AI-generated action must be traceable and auditable. This section defines the Human-in-the-Loop (HiTL) authorization gate, commitment records, the AUTHORIZE/PENDING_AUTH message flow, and the append-only audit log requirements for all AI-driven robots.">
  <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-4">
    <h1 class="mb-0">§16 AI Accountability</h1>
  </div>
  <div class="flex gap-2 mb-8 flex-wrap">
    <span class="inline-flex items-center px-2.5 py-0.5 rounded-full text-xs font-medium bg-green-500/10 text-green-400 border border-green-500/20">
      Status: Stable
    </span>
